{"tid":1631984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人！團結！光復香港，時代革命！","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T13:28:38.000Z","uid":222569,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4048912f9da5a1914627ecf849853480678a2be0","tid":1631984,"uid":222569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:43:58.000Z","msg":"由777宣佈緊急法開始，連登風向極混亂，兩走極端的post好多<br />\n<br />\n同步大家見到現場的畫面一樣<br />\n<br />\n黑警大量混入示威群眾，同五毛混入連登帶風一樣，總之要有咁亂得咁亂，令大家互相指責<br />\n<br />\n大家諗下，係咪似曾相識？<br />\n<br />\n雨傘運動立法會破璃打碎，旺角黑社會橫行等令運動打散<br />\n<br />\n魚蛋運動又係互相指責而失敗<br />\n<br />\n游梁，本民前，民族黨被dq, 大家割蓆，然後共狗全部過半，香港徹底淪亡<br />\n<br />\n呢4個月的運動，一樣經歷過好多分化危機，包括：<br />\n1. 6.9應唔應該留守煲底<br />\n2. 7.1應唔應該衝立法會<br />\n3. 8.18是否應該和理非遊行<br />\n4. 是否開始暫停圍狗屋<br />\n5. 是否需要化妝<br />\n6. 是否需要出魔法<br />\n7. 是否需要獅鳥<br />\n8. 是否需要大遊行<br />\n<br />\n大家經歷過好多事情先捱到呢一日，<br />\n被虐待，意見被無視，被抺黑，嫁禍，失蹤，自殺，嚴重受傷，言論自由收窄，被捕。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n總總事情大家都刻服了，大家現在面對更關鍵時間，如果團結成功，就會贏！林鄭己經無棋，如果大家都唔切割，林鄭已經無乜嘢可以做。<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日777押上經濟，交通不便的籌碼，希望民意逆轉，如果民情維持不變，777就會面對藍絲的反咬，因為佢哋會覺得呢個政府全能，黑警無能解決當下情況。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我哋更應團結，相信所有手足，出火魔法不割，裝修不割，阻止手足怕錯手殺死藍絲不割，獅鳥的不割，因為經歷左咁多事，我相信大家都睇到每事都有節有理，唔相信會突然失控。<br />\n<br />\n因此，團結所有的人，在黎明來到之前緊握大家雙手，一齊離開黑暗時間。<br />\n<br />\n香港人！團結！<br />\n<br />\n不分化，核彈都唔割。前線你放心去做。<br />\n<br />\n成功在望"},{"pid":"d8a4467384061fe92920a8cf3edf242509d4c7b9","tid":1631984,"uid":222569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:44:23.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"83f66e082f74c3fe2e0acc4dfaff12323ddaef58","tid":1631984,"uid":288707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:45:05.000Z","msg":"休養生息<br />\n人權法過左之後就係港共最虛弱既時候<br />\n到時再襯佢病攞佢命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e8883348aae310984af5fba3868d8d1c7dada0","tid":1631984,"uid":222569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:07:34.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"6734524a43c0a6291d246dc3b374ad64cbe56d23","tid":1631984,"uid":188657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:08:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f71cfb3893e8633bb2a4152077af05b60f3bddb","tid":1631984,"uid":188657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:10:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"281e54a0c47d8074250f601d1dda0ba60a73c94f","tid":1631984,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:11:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"379e15c6788531dccec5322cb041b6866c1b164a","tid":1631984,"uid":331388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:11:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a8246c506d16df51ace0d8964c2e5e0eda818e5","tid":1631984,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:14:57.000Z","msg":"形象工程！！！！<br />\n<br />\n[行動post] 10.7 爆食日 攪珠結果出爐<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632126</a>"},{"pid":"48f9c326ccaef94726169eadf8dc4bf43b5ee520","tid":1631984,"uid":188657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:19:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"daa7eb8ce64fe864da120e90fe7dc35f2bef9cbf","tid":1631984,"uid":222569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:54:47.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"6cb0398dcb799efd703447a9403e006f2df1e117","tid":1631984,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4048912f9da5a1914627ecf849853480678a2be0","tid":1631984,"uid":222569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:43:58.000Z","msg":"由777宣佈緊急法開始，連登風向極混亂，兩走極端的post好多<br />\n<br />\n同步大家見到現場的畫面一樣<br />\n<br />\n黑警大量混入示威群眾，同五毛混入連登帶風一樣，總之要有咁亂得咁亂，令大家互相指責<br />\n<br />\n大家諗下，係咪似曾相識？<br />\n<br />\n雨傘運動立法會破璃打碎，旺角黑社會橫行等令運動打散<br />\n<br />\n魚蛋運動又係互相指責而失敗<br />\n<br />\n游梁，本民前，民族黨被dq, 大家割蓆，然後共狗全部過半，香港徹底淪亡<br />\n<br />\n呢4個月的運動，一樣經歷過好多分化危機，包括：<br />\n1. 6.9應唔應該留守煲底<br />\n2. 7.1應唔應該衝立法會<br />\n3. 8.18是否應該和理非遊行<br />\n4. 是否開始暫停圍狗屋<br />\n5. 是否需要化妝<br />\n6. 是否需要出魔法<br />\n7. 是否需要獅鳥<br />\n8. 是否需要大遊行<br />\n<br />\n大家經歷過好多事情先捱到呢一日，<br />\n被虐待，意見被無視，被抺黑，嫁禍，失蹤，自殺，嚴重受傷，言論自由收窄，被捕。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n總總事情大家都刻服了，大家現在面對更關鍵時間，如果團結成功，就會贏！林鄭己經無棋，如果大家都唔切割，林鄭已經無乜嘢可以做。<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日777押上經濟，交通不便的籌碼，希望民意逆轉，如果民情維持不變，777就會面對藍絲的反咬，因為佢哋會覺得呢個政府全能，黑警無能解決當下情況。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我哋更應團結，相信所有手足，出火魔法不割，裝修不割，阻止手足怕錯手殺死藍絲不割，獅鳥的不割，因為經歷左咁多事，我相信大家都睇到每事都有節有理，唔相信會突然失控。<br />\n<br />\n因此，團結所有的人，在黎明來到之前緊握大家雙手，一齊離開黑暗時間。<br />\n<br />\n香港人！團結！<br />\n<br />\n不分化，核彈都唔割。前線你放心去做。<br />\n<br />\n成功在望"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:55:29.000Z","msg":"10.6大遊行國際風向整合︰未來半個月轉成和理非就可以輕鬆贏<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejmvwS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejmvwS</a>"},{"pid":"39c8dcade8187a3780c59b7f255c0435aa064cda","tid":1631984,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:56:02.000Z","msg":"「認真」各位手足 借東風啊！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629930</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n麻煩幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24365139eee47c1780be5a91c5669c5d395a8acb","tid":1631984,"uid":222569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:29:26.000Z","msg":"自推 4/10"},{"pid":"30ede868687d17094c80c343b172f72f150a8578","tid":1631984,"uid":222569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:26:14.000Z","msg":"自推 4/ 10 <br />\n<br />\n核彈都唔割！"},{"pid":"1ecef28e6fc0dad3eca8cf370e7926946921c2be","tid":1631984,"uid":252007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:28:38.000Z","msg":"唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}